                    <mxGeometry x="500" y="160" width="600" height="30" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ai2-step1" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: #F57C00;&quot;&gt;1. Job Description Analysis&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;b&gt;Model:&lt;/b&gt; Gemini 2.5 Pro&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Extract required skills and qualifications&lt;br&gt;• Identify ATS keywords&lt;br&gt;• Analyze company culture signals&lt;br&gt;• Generate gap analysis vs. user profile&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Output:&lt;/b&gt; Structured JD analysis JSON" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFE0B2;strokeColor=#F57C00;strokeWidth=2;align=left;fontSize=15;spacingLeft=15;fontStyle=0" parent="ai2-1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="510" y="210" width="280" height="170" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ai2-step2" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: #F57C00;&quot;&gt;2. Retrieval-Augmented Generation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;b&gt;Model:&lt;/b&gt; text-embedding-004&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Convert JD to 768-dim vector embedding&lt;br&gt;• Query pgvector database for similar stories&lt;br&gt;• Retrieve top-K relevant user narratives&lt;br&gt;• Return contextual examples&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Output:&lt;/b&gt; Ranked relevant stories" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFCC80;strokeColor=#F57C00;strokeWidth=2;align=left;fontSize=15;spacingLeft=15;fontStyle=0" parent="ai2-1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="810" y="190" width="280" height="180" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ai2-step3" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: #F57C00;&quot;&gt;3. Personality Integration&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;b&gt;Hybrid OCEAN Assessment&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• BFI-20 Likert Scale (70% weight)&lt;br&gt;• Gemini NLP Analysis (30% weight)&lt;br&gt;• Infer work style, communication preferences&lt;br&gt;• Tone and language adaptation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Output:&lt;/b&gt; Personality-driven content strategy" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFB74D;strokeColor=#F57C00;strokeWidth=2;align=left;fontSize=15;spacingLeft=15;fontStyle=0" parent="ai2-1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="510" y="400" width="280" height="160" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ai2-step4" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: #F57C00;&quot;&gt;4. Resume Generation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;b&gt;Model:&lt;/b&gt; Gemini 2.5 Pro&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Synthesize all inputs (profile, JD, stories, personality)&lt;br&gt;• Generate tailored resume content&lt;br&gt;• Optimize for ATS compatibility&lt;br&gt;• Apply personality-driven tone&lt;br&gt;• Format in professional markdown&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Output:&lt;/b&gt; Tailored resume markdown" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFA726;strokeColor=#F57C00;strokeWidth=2;align=left;fontSize=15;spacingLeft=15;fontStyle=0" parent="ai2-1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="810" y="400" width="280" height="190" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ai2-step5" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: #F57C00;&quot;&gt;5. PDF Generation &amp; Delivery&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rendering Engine:&lt;/b&gt; Puppeteer (Headless Chrome)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Convert markdown → HTML&lt;br&gt;• Apply professional template&lt;br&gt;• Generate print-optimized PDF&lt;br&gt;• Upload to Cloud Storage&lt;br&gt;• Deliver download link to user&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Output:&lt;/b&gt; Production-ready PDF resume" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FF9800;strokeColor=#F57C00;strokeWidth=2;align=left;fontSize=15;spacingLeft=15;fontStyle=0" parent="ai2-1" vertex="1">
