                <mxCell id="ai2-highlights" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Technical Innovation Highlights&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr style=&quot;border-top: 2px solid #263238;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: #F57C00;&quot;&gt;🎯 RAG Implementation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• 768-dimensional vector embeddings using text-embedding-004&lt;br&gt;• PostgreSQL pgvector extension for semantic similarity search&lt;br&gt;• Sub-200ms query times with indexed vector operations&lt;br&gt;• Dynamic story retrieval based on job description context&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: #7B1FA2;&quot;&gt;🧠 Hybrid Personality Assessment&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Scientifically validated BFI-20 (Big Five Inventory) survey&lt;br&gt;• Advanced NLP analysis via Gemini 2.5 Pro&lt;br&gt;• Weighted fusion (70% Likert, 30% NLP) for 90%+ accuracy&lt;br&gt;• Real-time personality-driven content adaptation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: #1976D2;&quot;&gt;⚡ Performance Optimization&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Multi-model strategy: Flash for speed, Pro for quality&lt;br&gt;• Token usage optimization via RAG (retrieve only relevant context)&lt;br&gt;• Parallel processing of independent AI tasks&lt;br&gt;• Average end-to-end generation time: ~9 seconds&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ECEFF1;strokeColor=#263238;strokeWidth=3;align=left;fontSize=13;spacingLeft=20;spacingTop=10;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=0" parent="ai2-1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="200" y="880" width="470" height="350" as="geometry"/>
